   </ul>\n\n                        \n                        <h1 class=\"c-article-title\" data-test=\"article-title\" data-article-title=\"\">Accessible design and testing in the application development process: considerations for an integrated approach</h1>\n                        <ul class=\"c-article-author-list js-etal-collapsed\" data-etal=\"25\" data-etal-small=\"3\" data-test=\"authors-list\" data-component-authors-activator=\"authors-list\"><li class=\"c-article-author-list__item\"><a data-test=\"author-name\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"open author\" data-track-label=\"link\" href=\"#auth-Gottfried-Zimmermann\" data-author-popup=\"auth-Gottfried-Zimmermann\" data-corresp-id=\"c1\">Gottfried Zimmermann<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"img\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon\"><use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" xlink:href=\"#global-icon-email\"></use></svg></a><sup class=\"u-js-hide\"><a href=\"#Aff1\">1</a></sup> &amp; </li><li class=\"c-article-author-list__item\"><a data-test=\"author-name\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"open author\" data-track-label=\"link\" href=\"#auth-Gregg-Vanderheiden\" data-author-popup=\"auth-Gregg-Vanderheiden\">Gregg Vanderheiden</a><sup class=\"u-js-hide\"><a href=\"#Aff2\">2</a></sup>\u00a0</li></ul>\n                        <p class=\"c-article-info-details\" data-container-section=\"info\">\n                            \n    <a data-test=\"journal-link\" href=\"/journal/10209\"><i data-test=\"journal-title\">Universal Access in the Information Society</i></a>\n\n                            <b data-test=\"journal-volume\"><span class=\"u-visually-hidden\">volume</span>\u00a07</b>,\u00a0<span class=\"u-visually-hidden\">pages </span>117\u2013128 (<span data-test=\"article-publication-year\">2008</span>)<a href=\"#citeas\" class=\"c-article-info-details__cite-as u-hide-print\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"cite this article\" data-track-label=\"link